        <sponsor name-id="S345">Mr. Johnson of Wisconsin</sponsor> (for himself and <cosponsor name-id="S327">Mr. Warner</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was read twice and referred to the <committee-name committee-id="SSFI00">Committee on Finance</committee-name>
